data.description: Welcome to this delightful home in the Crestwood neighborhood with no HOA!!! This residence offers an open floor plan, master on main and a 4th bedroom and full bathroom upstairs. Situated on just under a half-acre, beautiful, stacked stone, cedar shake finishes & an inviting rocking chair front porch. The foyer leads to a formal dining room perfect for gatherings that flows effortlessly into the kitchen and living room. This popular open concept wastes no space and connects the living spaces brilliantly for comfort, conversation and dining. The kitchen is designed with function and style featuring gleaming granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, crown molding on the cabinets, pendant lighting, a large pantry and an island perfect for entertaining. The living room is cozy and inviting with high ceilings and stacked stone fireplace. The split bedroom floor plan has the master suite located off of the main living space and the additional bedrooms to the opposite side of the home. The Master is generous in size with a connecting master bathroom featuring a large soaking tub, tile shower and double vanity sink, as well as a spacious walk-in closet. Each additional bedroom has ample closet space, plush carpet and includes ceiling fans. This lovely home has an oversized garage & list full of additional upgrades including new paint, flooring, tile finishes, kitchen backsplash, sod, gutter covers, outdoor ceiling fans and so much more. MOVE IN READY and includes a washer and dryer!!! Schedule your tour today, this could be your new home!!!
